Now that my daughter is getting older, she is all about dancing.  It's funny how my boys used to watch Angelina Ballerina and now my 2 year old daughter loves her.  This DVD is a cute collection of Angelina episodes that is sure to get any child up and moving.  They are episodes that have previously aired on television but it is nice to have them on one DVD.  The main episode is all about Spring and starting fresh, then there are some other cute ones included that are not necessarily Spring related.  There are cute lessons throughout the episodes perfect for young kids to grasp.

Episodes Include:

Angelinas Spring Fling
Angelina and the Front Page
Angelina and the New Jeans
Angelinas Trick-or-Treat Feat
Angelina and the Poster

The Stories on this Great New DVD are very Amazing! a Great Story about Springtime Traditions! A Great Story about Working together,even for the Newspaper. A Great Story about being there for a Friend. I do not want to give the rest away,but these Stories sure are Wonderful for all Children and their Family and Friends! 2 Big THumbs Up!!
